OL,3,CTen-year-old crowned best in the UK at
OL,4,Cfarming awards
OL,6,FA 10-year-old girl from Ceredigion has
OL,7,Fwon a prestigious award in the very
OL,8,Ffirst Young British Farming Awards.
OL,10,FElliw Grug Davies from Llanybydder has
OL,11,Fbeen named UK Junior Handler of the
OL,12,FYear after showing her bull, Urock, in
OL,13,Fthe competition.
OL,15,F"I'm so happy to win this award,"
OL,16,FElliw told ITV Cymru Wales.
OL,18,F"I couldn't believe it when they said
OL,19,F'Elliw Grug Davies' and I thought 'oh
OL,20,Fmy God, that's me'."
