OL,3,CTen-year-old crowned best in the UK at
OL,4,Cfarming awards
OL,6,FThe event, organised and run by the
OL,7,FFarmer's Guardian recognises British
OL,8,FFarmers and Agricultural businesses
OL,9,Ffor their commitment, resilience and
OL,10,Finnovation.
OL,12,FElliw enjoys helping her parents on
OL,13,Fthe farm and has ambitions of becoming
OL,14,Fa cow groomer when she grows up.
OL,16,FHer little brother Ioan is just as
OL,17,Fambitious and is learning the ropes
OL,18,Ffrom Elliw. He has his own bull calf
OL,19,Fcalled Victor, who is just two weeks
OL,20,Fold, and Ioan hopes to show him in the
OL,21,Fring in the future.
