OL,3,CTen-year-old crowned best in the UK at
OL,4,Cfarming awards
OL,6,FHowever, this isn't Elliw's first
OL,7,Fprize. After entering the show ring at
OL,8,Fjust four years old, she has a number
OL,9,Fof titles under her belt, including
OL,10,FJunior Young Handler at the Royal
OL,11,FWelsh Show with Dorset sheep.
OL,13,FElliw's mum, Elen, says her daughter
OL,14,Fremains surprisingly calm during
OL,15,Fcompetitions.
OL,17,F"I was more nervous than her you
OL,18,Fknow," Elen said. I was asking her on
OL,19,Fthe way up 'Are you ok?' 'Yes I'm
OL,20,Ffine!' It didn't flinch her at all you
OL,21,Fknow.
